					<p class="mb-4">ABC Learning is an excellent English learning website designed to help People improve their English skills easily and effectively. With an intuitive interface and diverse learning tools, ABC Learning provides learners with an excellent online learning environment.</p>
					<p class="mb-4">With ABC Learning, you can choose from a range of rich English courses that suit your level and personal goals. The courses are divided into levels from beginner to advanced, allowing you to start with basic knowledge and gradually progress to higher levels.</p>
					<div class="row gy-2 gx-4 mb-4">
						<div class="col-sm-6">
							<p class="mb-0"><i class="fa fa-arrow-right text-primary me-2"></i>English Good Web</p>
						</div>
						<div class="col-sm-6">
							<p class="mb-0"><i class="fa fa-arrow-right text-primary me-2"></i>Meeting Room</p>
						</div>
						<div class="col-sm-6">
							<p class="mb-0"><i class="fa fa-arrow-right text-primary me-2"></i>Quick Response</p>
						</div>
						<div class="col-sm-6">
							<p class="mb-0"><i class="fa fa-arrow-right text-primary me-2"></i>Search Dictionary</p>
						</div>
						<div class="col-sm-6">
							<p class="mb-0"><i class="fa fa-arrow-right text-primary me-2"></i>Learning Any Where</p>
						</div>
						<div class="col-sm-6">
							<p class="mb-0"><i class="fa fa-arrow-right text-primary me-2"></i>Quality Courses</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<a class="btn btn-primary py-3 px-5 mt-2" href="@Url.Action("About", "Home")">Read More</a>
